\cf2 \cb3 Within the main living space, a direct connection to the exterior is created through the implementation of a generously sized vertical window, allowing the view of the bay to be seen whilst the clients enjoy their casual hobby of cooking. As this opening is raised upwards, privacy at the street plane is created. Besides this, large apertures maximise the amount of natural sunlight penetrating the space, and this is also facilitated by the use of a skylight above the stairwell, in which the separation between the floating staircase allows light to pass through."}